title: Turok Dinosaur Hunter (Pc)
description:
Turok was one of the first fully 3-D shooters that was acclaimed for being something more than just another DOOM clone. It combined an interesting story with innovative level design and technically proficient graphics.

You will have to unzip the file.

If a window pop with information :
The program can't start because sgl2x.dll or sgl.sll is missing from your computer.
Try reinstalling the program to fix this problem.

Click two times start on the pop window. Ignore fix a error.

Start Turok

The game works
